THE MATRiX DEZiONiZED ~ 2nd edition (DVD5)

NTSC, Runtime: 143 minutes, Audio: English, German, French

&quot; I am going to show these people what you don't want them to see,
 I am going to show them the Matrix... without Zion.&quot; ~ Neo notsee

This is a special edition combining Matrix Reloaded and Matrix Revolutions
 to one complete movie. It is an unauthorized fanmade edition by the CBB group.

We came up with the idea to leave out Zion completely, to never have the Morpheus speech, nor the great battle, dance scene, prime minister, and especially no Commander Locke. This project was never spontaneous, it included a lot of planning and organizing and idea sharing. We tried to improve two movies that both were a major disappointment for the audience, but still they were very successful, so we had to put out something almost professional. The secret about a good fanedit is: it should never look or feel like a fanedit. Why so much effort? Because the MATRiX deserved to have a worthy sequel and because WE just love good movies and don't mind altering the not-so-good ones to suit our expectations.

Matrix DeZIONized CBB fanedit trailer:
v=Mc1RYDC6FIY

Original Runtime: 138 min &amp; 129 min
Amount of time Cut/Added: approx. 120 min cut
and 1 minute added from original THE MATRIX

